(16, 'Altered Carbon', 'Altered.Carbon@blank.com', 'yoga1234', '\"Balance, strength, flexibility, alignment, connectedness, joy, flow, reward, achievement, release, spiritual, commitment to myself... \"', 'Evening Class'),
(17, 'Big Quarry', 'Big.Quarry@blank.com', 'yoga1234', '\"One of the nicest things about Mayo Yoga sessions & Workshops is how all needs are met & everyone can progress at their own pace in a very safe & welcoming environment.\"', 'Evening Class'),
(18, 'Gamora Mulvaney', 'Gamora.Mulvaney@blank.com', 'yoga1234', '\"I love Danika\'s style of yoga, the class has a great pace I would recommend to anyone who likes a yoga class that has a good pace and a good chance for relaxation afterwards.\"', 'Evening Class'),
(19, 'Tony Stark', 'Tony.Stark@blank.com', 'yoga1234', '\"I have been going to Danika\'s classes for a few months now & I am always looking forward to my weekly class as it helps me to de-stress. The general perception is that Yoga is mostly practiced by women, I would highly recommend Danika.\"', 'Evening Class'),
(20, 'Eddie Murphy', 'Eddie.Murphy@blank.com', 'yoga1234', '\"The yoga instructor, Danika is brilliant. She is very thorough and ensures that you are doing the moves correctly. Such a great class, I love it\"', 'Evening Class'),
(21, 'Scott Lang', 'Scott.Lang@blank.com', 'yoga1234', '\"I\' absolutely love Mayo Yoga. Since starting yoga earlier this year, both me & my physio have observed noticeable improvement in my flexibility.  Classes are great for focusing the mind & body. Highly recommended.\"', 'Evening Class'),
(22, 'Steve Rogers', 'Steve.Rogers@blank.com', 'yoga1234', '\"I\'m only a beginner but after doing Mayo Yoga with Danika. I don\'t think I could go anywhere else! What a brilliant teacher! Would recommend Mayo Yoga to anyone I love it :)\"', 'Evening Class'),
(23, 'Peter Quill', 'Peter.Quill@blank.com', 'yoga1234', '\"I found that this class has supported me physically.  As I wanted I had a drug free birth using only yoga and breathing. I highly recommend Mayo Yoga  yoga class, as a supportive and uplifting experience for any mother to be. Thank you Danika for a wonderful experience, and being at the beginning of my yoga road.\"', 'Pregnancy Class'),
(24, 'Ann-Marie Rochcough', 'Ann-Marie.Rochcough@blank.com', 'yoga1234', '\"Thank you for the pregnancy course. I can\'t tell you how much I enjoyed it and also how much help the breathing techniques were\"', 'Pregnancy Class'),
(25, 'Janet Van-Damme', 'Janet.Van-Damme@blank.com', 'yoga1234', '\"I really enjoyed the pregnancy yoga classes & I always felt great afterwards. Thank you!\"', 'Pregnancy Class'),
(26, 'Aine Burke', 'Aine.Burke@blank.com', 'yoga1234', '\"I would highly recommend Danika\'s class to expectant mums as she created a very relaxed and enjoyable class\"', 'Pregnancy Class'),
(27, 'James O\'Reilly', 'James.O\'Reilly@blank.com', 'yoga1234', '\"Thanks for all your help and advice, I really think the yoga helped me through the pregnancy and labour.\"', 'Pregnancy Class'),
(28, 'Catherine Thanos', 'Catherine.Thanos@blank.com', 'yoga1234', '\"I attended Danika\'s yoga classes prior to my pregnancy and then during. I love the friendly, caring, fun and relaxed atmosphere that Danika creates. I love her style of teaching and the level of yoga is perfect.\"', 'Pregnancy Class'),
(29, 'Katarzyna Romanov', 'Katarzyna.Romanov@blank.com', 'yoga1234', '\"I am very satisfied with the results of my Reiki sessions with Danika. I attended four consecutive Reiki sessions which improved my condition dramatically. The first two sessions were quite tough, clearing the accumulated bad energy. Then the following two sessions gave my spirit a fresh boost of positive energy. It was a unique experience and I would very much recommend it to everyone ready for it.\"', 'Reiki'),
(30, 'Drax Clean', 'Drax.Clean@blank.com', 'yoga1234', '\"I have been attending Reiki sessions since November 2014 with Danika. My sessions have been very emotional & powerful & they have given me the strength to deal with many personal strifes that I have faced & to let them go. Coupled with my regular yoga practice with Danika, there is a balance in my life & my mind is clearer & ready to face life\'s challenges. Thanks Danika\"', 'Reiki'),
(31, 'Sabrina Witch', 'Sabrina.Witch@blank.com', 'yoga1234', '\"I\'d heard of Reiki before but I had really no idea what it entailed. If I\'m honest I was very skeptical it would actually work, but desperate to feel like the old me again I said I\'d give it a shot. The first session was so overwhelming, dealing with the past is something I\'d been too busy to ever do. Apart from the significant improvement physically, I was more surprised by how it affected me emotionally. It has definitely made me more relaxed and content, I\'m much more aware of what\'s important to me in life now. I feel Reiki has helped me start a new chapter of my life and I\'m looking forward to the future. Thank you so much : ))\"', 'Reiki'),
(32, 'John Silver', 'John.Silver@blank.com', 'yoga1234', '\"I had been going to Danika\'s yoga class for over a year and really enjoy her classes. I had told Danika about what had happened and it was actually her that suggested that Reiki could be very useful for me. I did not know very much about Reiki but I had 100% trust in Danika as I had learnt a lot from her in yoga and respected her advise. I found Reiki extremely powerful and so useful in helping me through a very difficult time in my life. I want to thank Danika so much for her help and support over the past few months, she truly has helped me to become balanced again and be positive about the future.\"', 'Reiki'),
(33, 'Karen Banks', 'Karen.Banks@blank.com', 'yoga1234', '\"As a newcomer to Mayo Yoga Studio I was delighted to have the opportunity to attend Danika\'s workshop on Feb 22nd. I found the experience to be calming yet energizing. The homemade cakes, tea and little chats with fellow yogi\'s was a lovely way to end the workshop. I\'ve already signed up for Danika\'s next workshop on April 26!\"', 'Workshop'),
(34, 'Nikoleta Minix', 'Nikoleta.Minix@blank.com', 'yoga1234', '\"Well balanced three hours of yoga were full of moments where the feelings of joy and satisfaction were jostling out to the surface. The icing on the cake was the very last part, meditation where Danika\'s voice was leading us through the last half an hour and I felt like my mind left the body. Danika thank you for the beautiful experience topped by the goodies at the end.\"', 'Workshop'),
(35, 'Luke Cage', 'Luke.Cage@blank.com', 'yoga1234', '\"Balance, strength, flexibility, alignment, connectedness, joy, flow, reward, achievement, release, spiritual, commitment to myself...\"', 'Workshop'),
(36, 'Joan Arc', 'Joan.Arc@blank.com', 'yoga1234', '\"Thanks Danika, for a wonderful afternoon of total relaxation, thoroughly enjoyed both workshops that I attended at your studio, can\'t wait for the next one, definitely a mind changing experience.\"', 'Workshop'),
(37, 'Jean Grey', 'Jean.Grey@blank.com', 'yoga1234', '\"Danika, I would like to thank you for a fantastic day. Your yoga workshop was THE BEST yoga experience I have ever had.  Namaste.\"', 'Workshop'),
(38, 'Gabe Logan', 'Gabe.Logan@blank.com', 'yoga1234', '\"The workshop was a thorough workout for the brain & body while fully relaxing me. I felt great & totally relaxed after it.\"', 'Workshop'),
(42, 'Scott Summers', 'Scott.Summers@mail.ie', '9953914e25494783a44937f93016b8be', 'this is the test user review submited in the review page form', 'Corporate Class');
